    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create multiple weapons made out of Chakra and hurl them at your opponent. Select two weapons and make a number of ranged Ninjutsu attacks equal to the number of weapons created towards a creature of your choice within range. On a hit, you deal the weapon's damage die + your Ninjutsu modifier and apply any properties it may have.</p><p data-start=\"337\" data-end=\"480\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node><strong data-start=\"337\" data-end=\"357\">At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this Jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost by 3 and increase the number of weapons you create by 1.</p>",
